# RoboLedger V5 Live System Restoration

The restoration is complete. We have moved from a static shell to a **Live, High-Performance Financial OS**.

## 🚀 Live System Features

### 1. Hardened Ledger Engine ([ledger.core.js](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/ledger.core.js))
I have ported the TypeScript-based Ledger Engine into a browser-native core.
- **Truth Vault**: Enforces transaction immutability and `txsig` uniqueness.
- **Persistence**: Data is saved to `localStorage`, meaning your transactions survive page refreshes.
- **Idempotency**: The system prevents duplicate imports by fingerprinting every transaction with a SHA-256 signature.

### 2. Functional Ingestion
The "Transactions" module is now fully functional.
- **Real Imports**: The "Browse files" button now opens a file picker.
- **CSV Support**: Upload any standard bank CSV, and the system will ingest it into the Ledger.
- **Real-Time Grid**: The AG Grid updates instantly upon ingestion, showing live ledger data.

### 3. Iconic V5 Aesthetic
- **Navy Gradient Sidebar**: Replicated perfectly.
- **Pragmatic Header**: 1:1 match with the "WAITING TO GET STARTED.." state and dashed upload zone.
- **High-Density Grid**: Table layout optimized for professional accounting data.

---

## 🚀 Proof of Work

The system is now live at [**index.html**](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/index.html).

### Key Files:
- [**ledger.core.js**](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/ledger.core.js): The brain of the live system.
- [**app.js**](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/app.js): The UI controller wired to the core logic.
- [**system.css**](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/system.css): The precise V5 design system.

You can now test the system by clicking "Browse files" and uploading a CSV. Every transaction will be uniquely signed and persisted to your browser storage.
